  <p style="margin-top:18px;">4 of the top 5 reach posts are humorous, self-deprecating content riding on Vietnamese meme/pop-culture trends — not traditional recruitment announcements. This is exactly what explains "Other": <b style="color:var(--ink)">a distinct tone of voice that is outperforming everything else, yet hasn't been formally recognized as its own pillar.</b> Post #1 reached nearly 6x the page's average Reach/Post (3,679).</p>

